{"tid":293271,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★頭先睇 納粹達豪集中營，仲以為描述香港現況！","createTime":"2017-06-22T04:35:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-25T08:55:20.000Z","uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8656ff08cb4c5e1db8290a13fa3a520cd89bdf00","tid":293271,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T04:35:49.000Z","msg":"在達豪集中營，囚犯要一天至少勞動9到11個小時，每周沒有休息日。只有犯人高燒超過了40度或站不起來了，才可以停止勞動。「勞動使人自由」變成了「勞改直至死亡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/large/6723/7135956800\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2Flarge%2F6723%2F7135956800&h=2f023274&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鐵門上鑄造了兩行大字：「ARBEIT MACHT FREI」（「勞動使人自由！」）。這是達豪集中營最著名的口號，出自德國作家Lorenz Diefenbach作於1872年的小說《勞動使人自由》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/history/n63m85.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fhistory%2Fn63m85.html&d=17n4cqxg%2B2J6khD3gA7q%2BHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=b0a447d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/history/n63m85.html</a>"},{"pid":"4289e979735b685d2d205b2620df1df14b152aeb","tid":293271,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T04:36:34.000Z","msg":"香港工時仲長過佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5832da6e0ce3dc5ea9891ad886b4e69c258fc17","tid":293271,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T04:36:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2633c92fe7deb4e2bc74535e512669b36fc35a94","tid":293271,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T04:37:14.000Z","msg":"證明返工為人類核心價值<br />\n樓豬請返工"},{"pid":"5b0292ab1f6cb0ccd9bb29c21bd2f61f9203e20f","tid":293271,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,