 />\n<br />\n<br />\n當列車行到奧斯維辛時，無數民眾被趕下了火車，變態的屠殺者們知道嘈雜慌亂的環境會影響人們進入毒氣室的速度，所以，他們為無辜的民眾編織了一個謊言。人們走在裝飾著綠色草坪邊的小道，通往納粹黨「好心」為旅客們提供的接風洗塵的「浴室」，旅客們安靜的走在路上，被靜謐的環境吸引。他們走進被安排的房間，心中滿意，但隨著房間人數的不斷增多，以至於到擁擠不堪時，一聲鳴響，大鐵門被關閉的聲音沉重地擊打在所有人的心裡。燈光忽然被滅，人們開始恐慌尖叫，看守在門外的納粹士兵開始向隱藏在綠色草坪里被民眾認為是白蘑菇的通氣孔里投放毒氣，毒氣通過通氣孔進入到房間，在噴頭下面的人開始搖晃著倒下，人們意識到不妙，開始爭先恐後的往門口涌去，所有人發出一聲聲的慘叫......<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/story/aejnmnn.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fstory%2Faejnmnn.html&d=17n4cqxg%2B2J6khD3gA7q%2BHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=92169fbc\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/story/aejnmnn.html</a>"},{"pid":"6d3670d2166534bcdb9cf935318dbcd5bf3ac4ce","tid":293271,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T05:00:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>奶波魔仲未入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nx2"},{"pid":"59d7be0c2e8f2e9fcb4e4d09770404c2eaeb9116","tid":293271,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T05:10:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>奶波魔仲未入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nx2</blockquote><br />\n蓋清都未入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"150d2f525ce743747f6c9d31d2ff5964d4d40489","tid":293271,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T05:12:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>奶波魔仲未入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nx2</blockquote><br />\n蓋清都未入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ndie左？"},{"pid":"bb6f297871baa3ac8629917695c1dcf8e64e7c83","tid":293271,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T05:17:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>奶波魔仲未入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nx2</blockquote><br />\n蓋清都未入<img src=\"/assets/fa